msgstr "https://publishpress.com/capability-manager/"

#: capsman-enhanced.php
#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"PublishPress Capabilities is the access control plugin for WordPress. You "
"can manage all your WordPress user roles, from Administrators to "
"Subscribers."
msgstr ""
"PublishPress Capaciteiten is de toegang controle plugin voor WordPress. Je "
"kunt al je WordPress gebruikersrollen beheren, van beheerders tot abonnees."

#: capsman-enhanced.php
#. Author of the plugin
msgid "PublishPress"
msgstr "PublishPress"

#: capsman-enhanced.php
#. Author URI of the plugin
